BOJ Keeps Key Overnight Rate Near Zero

-- B y   M a y u m i   O t s u m a
-- 
2011-06-14T03:43:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/bank-of-japan-keeps-key-overnight-rate-near-zero-credit-program-unchanged.html
The  Bank of Japan (8301)  held the benchmark
interest rate at a range of zero to 0.1 percent and kept
unchanged a 30 trillion yen ($374 billion) credit program and a
10-trillion yen asset-purchase fund that represent its main
policy tools. The central bank announced its policy decision in
a statement today in Tokyo.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mayumi Otsuma in Tokyo at 
 motsuma@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Lily Nonomiya at 
 lnonomiya@bloomberg.net  